-- Description:
-- Simple blink-a-led program for Microchip pic16f1784
-- using the internal oscillator.
-- The LED should be flashing twice a second!
--
-- Sources:
--
-- Notes:
--  - Creation date/time: 27 Mar 2014 21:28:44.
--  - This file is generated by "blink-a-led.cmd" script! Do not change!
